                            <comment id="13027427" author="tlipcon" created="Sun, 1 May 2011 05:10:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch which converts master.jsp and also adds a basic unit test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13027762" author="stack" created="Mon, 2 May 2011 18:44:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good to me (I like the test).  Will I bring over the other pages to use jamon?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13027778" author="tlipcon" created="Mon, 2 May 2011 19:10:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yea, I was planning on moving some more pages over if people seemed to like this choice. Let me ping the dev list and make sure a quorum of committers is on board, since it&apos;s something we will live with for a while.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13028058" author="tlipcon" created="Tue, 3 May 2011 06:07:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seems like people like this. I will move some of the other JSPs as well and post a patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13028076" author="tlipcon" created="Tue, 3 May 2011 07:02:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch which moves master and region server both to servlets with Jamon-based templates.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I didn&apos;t do zk.jsp yet. Maybe someone else wants to try it to get the hang of jamon? &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13028337" author="stack" created="Tue, 3 May 2011 17:40:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 Commit and I&apos;ll have a go at zk.jsp.  Thanks Todd.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13028370" author="tlipcon" created="Tue, 3 May 2011 19:05:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rebased on trunk. Will commit&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13030205" author="hudson" created="Sat, 7 May 2011 00:08:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in HBase-TRUNK #1909 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/hudson/job/HBase-TRUNK/1909/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/hudson/job/HBase-TRUNK/1909/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="13030911" author="lars_francke" created="Mon, 9 May 2011 21:36:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure about all the legal talk but perhaps one of you native speakers knows better: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.apache.org/legal/resolved.html#category-b&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.apache.org/legal/resolved.html#category-b&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13030937" author="stack" created="Mon, 9 May 2011 22:57:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@Lars I need to add a mention to NOTICES.txt about Jamon.  Here is its license: &lt;a href=&quot;http://jamonapi.sourceforge.net/JAMonLicense.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jamonapi.sourceforge.net/JAMonLicense.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13488114" author="vanto" created="Wed, 31 Oct 2012 19:11:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I stumbled upon this accidentally. I hope you didn&apos;t include the linked license to NOTICE.txt, since JAMon != Jamon. The former is a monitoring tool, the later is said template language. It is published under Mozilla Public License.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13488139" author="tlipcon" created="Wed, 31 Oct 2012 19:32:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like our current LICENSE.txt doesn&apos;t mention jamon at all, which is an oversight. It seems we should be calling it out as Mozilla Public License in our NOTICE.txt.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13489597" author="stack" created="Fri, 2 Nov 2012 17:57:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=vanto&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;vanto&quot;&gt;Tammo van Lessen&lt;/a&gt; I added a mention to our NOTICE.txt file that jamon the template engine is MPL (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7087&quot; title=&quot;Add to NOTICE.txt a note on jamon being MPL&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-7087&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-7087&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;).  Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15017039" author="lars_francke" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 12:41:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue was closed as part of a bulk closing operation on 2015-11-20. All issues that have been resolved and where all fixVersions have been released have been closed (following discussions on the mailing list).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
